1n tr&ecirc;n c\\u1ea3 m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 b&agrave;n v&agrave; thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng th&iacute;ch \\u1ee9ng c\\u1ee7a HTML5 l&agrave;m cho m\\u1ecdi th\\u1ee9 d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng h\\u01a1n khi x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng trang web.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">C&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i ho\\u1eb7c c\\u1eadp nh\\u1eadt ho\\u1ea1t \\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ebfn c&aacute;c ph\\u1ea7n kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n trang web c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch s\\u1eafp x\\u1ebfp ch&uacute;ng th&agrave;nh c&aacute;c t\\u1ec7p b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch h\\u1ee3p l&yacute; v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 do th\\u1ebb HTML \\u0111\\u01b0a ra.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">HTML5 \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng ngay t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1ea7u v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t API t\\u1ec7p nhanh h\\u01a1n v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef c\\u1ee5c b\\u1ed9 trong Flash.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"meta_title\":\"Di Chuy\\u1ec3n H\\u1ec7 Th\\u1ed1ng Gi\\u00e1o D\\u1ee5c\",\"meta_keywords\":\"NTTData, Di chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c\",\"meta_description\":\"Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn n\\u1ed9i dung gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c (K12) t\\u1eeb Flash sang HTML5\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"Education System Migration\",\"intro\":\"Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/system2\\\" style=\\\"height:50%; width:50%\\\" \\/><\