le=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Kh&ocirc;ng nghi ng\\u1edd g&igrave; n\\u1eefa, c&aacute;c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u sinh t\\u1ed3n &amp; thu\\u1ed1c men c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n t\\u1eeb tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ebfn nay ch\\u01b0a bao gi\\u1edd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u0103m s&oacute;c t\\u1ed1t nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec1u g&igrave; khi\\u1ebfn ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch Cura?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Cura l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n theo d&otilde;i h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng qua nhi\\u1ec1u t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng h\\u1eefu &iacute;ch. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 truy c\\u1eadp v&agrave;o h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 th\\u1ed1ng k&ecirc; s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ec7nh nh&acirc;n trong m\\u1ed9t kho\\u1ea3ng th\\u1eddi gian d\\u01b0\\u1edbi d\\u1ea1ng bi\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 cho ph&eacute;p \\u0111&aacute;p \\u1ee9ng thu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n. H\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa, Cura c&ograve;n l&agrave; l\\u1eddi nh\\u1eafc nh\\u1edf c&aacute; nh&acirc;n v\\u1ec1 vi\\u1ec7c u\\u1ed1ng thu\\u1ed1c v&agrave; ki\\u1ec3m tra s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3. Trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p kh\\u1ea9n c\\u1ea5p, vi\\u1ec7c t&igrave;m ki\\u1ebfm c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;m \\/ d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 y t\\u1ebf g\\u1ea7n nh\\u1ea5t c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 c&oacute; &iacute;ch cho vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb k\\u1ecbp th\\u1eddi. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng kh&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n bao g\\u1ed3m truy xu\\u1ea5t c&aacute;c b&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1ecdc l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed v&agrave; bi\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u1ed3 (l&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn 14 b&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1ecdc) cho m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh NEWS &amp; g\\u1eedi c&aacute;c b&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1ecdc l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed qua email ho\\u1eb7c MMS t\\u1edbi GP \\/ Caregiver.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"Cura - \\u1ee8ng D\\u1ee5ng Ch\\u0103m S\\u00f3c S\\u1ee9c Kh\\u1ecfe C\\u00e1 Nh\\u00e2n\",\"meta_keywords\":\"Cura,\\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n\",\"meta_description\":\"Nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ea5y d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 y t\\u1ebf lu\\u00f4n c\\u00f3 t\\u1ea7m quan tr\\u1ecdng l\\u1edbn, Cura cung c\\u1ea5p kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng truy c\\u1eadp di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0o th\\u00f4ng tin s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c y t\\u1ebf th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. M\\u1ed9t ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ec7n kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f2n qu\\u00e1 xa t\\u1ea7m v\\u1edbi!\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion\",\"intro\":\"As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/cura.webp\\\" style=\\\"height:50%; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Why do you need Cura?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Cura was designed for special benefit of users, aiming at better experiences and outcomes in medical care. Cura is the perfect replacement for messy hardcopy records, or multiple outdated forms of personal health check. This app is the reasonable transformation of health care, as technology has taken the stand over the years in many fields. Instead of loads of paper records, all information on your medical history is kept together in one easily accessible place, and as many records are kept as possible.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">This app can be utilised for public use among family members, relatives, rather than just limited personal use.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">For better understanding &amp; illustration, graphing feature offers an overview of general health status, which means users can see multiple spots simultaneously, then zoom to specific ranges and identify points of interest.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Best of all, Cura allows you to share your health records with your doctors at your own discretion, enhancing interaction at an accessible convenience.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Undoubtedly, your vital signs &amp; medication have never been taken such good care of so far!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">What makes users love Cura?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Cura is a mobile app that empowers you to keep track of your own health records through many helpful features. Users can have access to a record of patient health stats over a period in form of charts to enable better medication response. Moreover, Cura serves as a personal reminder for medication and periodical health check. In case of emergency, finding the nearest clinic\\/medical services from the location may come in handy for timely treatment. Other features to better user experience includes retrieving historical readings and chart (up to 14 readings) for NEWS monitors &amp; sending historical readings through email or MMS to GP\\/Caregiver.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"Cura\",\"meta_keywords\":\"Cura\",\"meta_description\":\"As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!\"}}',	'2022-07-21 15:55:53',	'2022-07-21 15:55:53'),
