(134,	'posts',	'updated',	328,	'Modules\\Article\\Entities\\Post',	2,	'App\\Models\\User',	'{\"attributes\":{\"name\":\"EHR - Electronic Health Record\",\"intro\":\"Electronic Health Record (EHR) is a mobile application that enables you to keep track of your own health records for healthier lifestyle & appropriate treatment. EHR has revolutionized the way modern people take care of themselves.\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/erth.webp\\\" style=\\\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\\\" \\/><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Why do you need EHR App?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">In daily busy life, everyone is now having less time spent on personal health care, yet this remains a problem of great concern. However, it seems unnecessary to have a personal nurse\\/ assistant to be in charge of this task. This is now the time for EHR to do the job. There&rsquo;ll no longer be doubts as to how much money\\/ what kind of treatment you may receive according to insurance policies, which drug you&rsquo;re allergic to, when to have your next periodical check-up or medication intakes.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Unlike most other health record applications, we know how to deal with security &amp; privacy issue by generating a unique OTP (one time password) so that you can choose your own doctor to have access to your health records through secured authentication. EHR creates a platform between doctors and patients to share a journal on check-ups, medication intakes. Best of all, EHR.sg allows you to share your health records with your doctors at your own discretion. Generating a unique OTP (one time password) via the app, doctors of your choice has access to your health records through secured authentication.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">EHR eliminates the need for profuse paper records and outdated forms &amp; replaces them with completely accurate &amp; reliable data.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">What makes users love EHR?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">This mobile application allows users to see their personal health records on drug allergies, insurance policies, health issues, current medications, history &amp; upcoming check-up appointments. One time password (OTP) can be generated each time patient needs to consult a doctor via website. Within minutes of downloading the app &amp; signing in with your own account, you&rsquo;re ready to use a fully featured and certified EHR.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"EHR - Electronic Health Record\",\"meta_keywords\":\"EHR,Electronic Health Record\",\"meta_description\":\"Electronic Health Record (EHR) is a mobile application that enables you to keep track of your own health records for healthier lifestyle & appropriate treatment. EHR has revolutionized the way modern people take care of themselves.\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"EHR - H\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 y t\\u1ebf \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed\",\"intro\":\"H\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed (EHR) l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cho ph\\u00e9p b\\u1ea1n theo d\\u00f5i h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00ednh m\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 l\\u1ed1i s\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e0nh m\\u1ea1nh h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. EHR \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00e1ch m\\u1ea1ng h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1ch con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/erth.webp\\\" style=\\\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">T\\u1ea1i sao b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n \\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng EHR?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Trong cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng b\\u1eadn r\\u1ed9n h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y, m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng &iacute;t d&agrave;nh th\\u1eddi gian cho vi\\u1ec7c ch\\u0103m s&oacute;c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111&acirc;y v\\u1eabn l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi quan t&acirc;m. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n ch&uacute;ng ta kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft ph\\u1ea3i c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t y t&aacute; \\/ tr\\u1ee3 l&yacute; ri&ecirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ee5 tr&aacute;ch c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c n&agrave;y. \\u0110&acirc;y l&agrave; th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ec3 EHR th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c. B\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng ph\\u1ea3i suy ngh\\u0129 v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ed1 ti\\u1ec1n \\/ h&igrave;nh th\\u1ee9c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb m&agrave; b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c theo ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b\\u1ea3o hi\\u1ec3m, lo\\u1ea1i thu\\u1ed1c b\\u1ea1n b\\u1ecb d\\u1ecb \\u1ee9ng, th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m kh&aacute;m s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ee3t d&ugrave;ng thu\\u1ed1c ti\\u1ebfp theo.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Kh&ocirc;ng gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 h\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft c&aacute;c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe kh&aacute;c, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i bi\\u1ebft c&aacute;ch gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt v&agrave; quy\\u1ec1n ri&ecirc;ng t\\u01b0 b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch t\\u1ea1o m\\u1ed9t OTP (m\\u1eadt kh\\u1ea9u d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n) duy nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn b&aacute;c s\\u0129 c\\u1ee7a ri&ecirc;ng m&igrave;nh, c&oacute; quy\\u1ec1n truy c\\u1eadp v&agrave;o h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n th&ocirc;ng qua x&aacute;c th\\u1ef1c b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt. EHR t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng gi\\u1eefa b&aacute;c s\\u0129 v&agrave; b\\u1ec7nh nh&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ec3 chia s\\u1ebb nh\\u1eadt k&yacute; v\\u1ec1 qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ki\\u1ec3m tra, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thu\\u1ed1c. H\\u01a1n h\\u1ebft, EHR.sg cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n chia s\\u1ebb h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh v\\u1edbi b&aacute;c s\\u0129 theo quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a ri&ecirc;ng b\\u1ea1n. T\\u1ea1o m\\u1ed9t OTP duy nh\\u1ea5t (m\\u1eadt kh\\u1ea9u d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n) th&ocirc;ng qua \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng, c&aacute;c b&aacute;c s\\u0129 m&agrave; b\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ecdn c&oacute; quy\\u1ec1n truy c\\u1eadp v&agrave;o h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n th&ocirc;ng qua x&aacute;c th\\u1ef1c b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">EHR lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf nhu c\\u1ea7u v\\u1ec1 h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 gi\\u1ea5y th\\u1eeba v&agrave; c&aacute;c bi\\u1ec3u m\\u1eabu l\\u1ed7i th\\u1eddi &amp; thay th\\u1ebf ch&uacute;ng b\\u1eb1ng d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c v&agrave; \\u0111&aacute;ng tin c\\u1eady.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec1u g&igrave; khi\\u1ebfn ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch EHR?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">\\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng xem h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd v\\u1ec1 d\\u1ecb \\u1ee9ng thu\\u1ed1c, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b\\u1ea3o hi\\u1ec3m, c&aacute;c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe, thu\\u1ed1c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i, ti\\u1ec1n s\\u1eed v&agrave; c&aacute;c cu\\u1ed9c h\\u1eb9n kh&aacute;m s\\u1eafp t\\u1edbi. M\\u1eadt kh\\u1ea9u d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n (OTP) c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o m\\u1ed7i khi b\\u1ec7nh nh&acirc;n c\\u1ea7n h\\u1ecfi &yacute; ki\\u1ebfn \\u200b\\u200bb&aacute;c s\\u0129 qua trang web. Trong v&ograve;ng v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t sau khi t\\u1ea3i xu\\u1ed1ng \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng v&agrave; \\u0111\\u0103ng nh\\u1eadp b\\u1eb1ng t&agrave;i kho\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a ri&ecirc;ng b\\u1ea1n, b\\u1ea1n \\u0111&atilde; s\\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng EHR \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"EHR - H\\u1ed3 S\\u01a1 Y T\\u1ebf \\u0111i\\u1ec7n T\\u1eed\",\"meta_keywords\":\"EHR,H\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 y t\\u1ebf \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed\",\"meta_description\":\"H\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed (EHR) l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cho ph\\u00e9p b\\u1ea1n theo d\\u00f5i h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00ednh m\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 l\\u1ed1i s\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e0nh m\\u1ea1nh h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. EHR \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00e1ch m\\u1ea1ng h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1ch con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.\"}}',	'2022-07-22 08:59:43',	'2022-07-22 08:59:43'),
(135,	'posts',	'updated',	327,	'Modules\\Article\\Entities\\Post',	2,	'App\\Models\\User',	'{\"attributes\":{\"name\":\"Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion\",\"intro\":\"As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/cura.webp\\\" style=\\\"height:50%; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Why do you need Cura?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Cura was designed for special benefit of users, aiming at better experiences and outcomes in medical care. Cura is the perfect replacement for messy hardcopy records, or multiple outdated forms of personal health check. This app is the reasonable transformation of health care, as technology has taken the stand over the years in many fields. Instead of loads of paper records, all information on your medical history is kept together in one easily accessible place, and as many records are kept as possible.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">This app can be utilised for public use among family members, relatives, rather than just limited personal use.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">For better understanding &amp; illustration, graphing feature offers an overview of general health status, which means users can see multiple spots simultaneously, then zoom to specific ranges and identify points of interest.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Best of all, Cura allows you to share your health records with your doctors at your own discretion, enhancing interaction at an accessible convenience.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Undoubtedly, your vital signs &amp; medication have never been taken such good care of so far!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">What makes users love Cura?<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Cura is a mobile app that empowers you to keep track of your own health records through many helpful features. Users can have access to a record of patient health stats over a period in form of charts to enable better medication response. Moreover, Cura serves as a personal reminder for medication and periodical health check. In case of emergency, finding the nearest clinic\\/medical services from the location may come in handy for timely treatment. Other features to better user experience includes retrieving historical readings and chart (up to 14 readings) for NEWS monitors &amp; sending historical readings through email or MMS to GP\\/Caregiver.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion\",\"meta_keywords\":\"Cura,Personal Healthcare Companion\",\"meta_description\":\"As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"Cura - \\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n\",\"intro\":\"Nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ea5y d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 y t\\u1ebf lu\\u00f4n c\\u00f3 t\\u1ea7m quan tr\\u1ecdng l\\u1edbn, Cura cung c\\u1ea5p kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng truy c\\u1eadp di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0o th\\u00f4ng tin s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c y t\\u1ebf th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. M\\u1ed9t ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh ch\\u0103m s