(143,	'posts',	'updated',	298,	'Modules\\Article\\Entities\\Post',	2,	'App\\Models\\User',	'{\"attributes\":{\"name\":\"Education System Migration\",\"intro\":\"Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5\",\"content\":\"<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/system2\\\" style=\\\"height:50%; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Client: <\\/strong>A trusted global innovator of IT and business services headquartered in Tokyo, help clients transform through consulting, industry solutions, business process services, IT modernization and managed services.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Business needs:&nbsp;<\\/strong>Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Features:<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">HTML5 has greatly reduced the limitations of flash ever since it was first introduced to the market. HTML5 can provide animations with better compatibility for more browsers on both desktops and mobile devices with proper use.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">The adaptive features of HTML5 make everything easier when one is building websites.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">Developers can easily change or update their animations without affecting other parts of their sites by properly organizing them into external files with specific instructions given by HTML tags.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">HTML5 has been built from the ground up with a faster and simpler file API than local storage in a flash.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"meta_title\":\"Education System Migration\",\"meta_keywords\":\"NTTData, Education System Migration\",\"meta_description\":\"Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5\"},\"old\":{\"name\":\"Di chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c\",\"intro\":\"Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn n\\u1ed9i dung gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c (K12) t\\u1eeb Flash sang HTML5\",\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng:<\\/strong> M\\u1ed9t nh&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi \\u0111&aacute;ng tin c\\u1eady tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n c\\u1ea7u v\\u1ec1 c&aacute;c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 CNTT v&agrave; kinh doanh c&oacute; tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch&iacute;nh t\\u1ea1i Tokyo, gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i th&ocirc;ng qua t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n, gi\\u1ea3i ph&aacute;p ng&agrave;nh, d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 quy tr&igrave;nh kinh doanh, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i h&oacute;a CNTT v&agrave; c&aacute;c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute;.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"\\/storage\\/files\\/Case studies\\/system2\\\" style=\\\"height:50%; width:50%\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\"><strong>Nhu c\\u1ea7u kinh doanh:<\\/strong> Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i h&agrave;ng ngh&igrave;n n\\u1ed9i dung gi&aacute;o d\\u1ee5c (K12) t\\u1eeb Flash sang HTML5<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng:<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:16px\\\">HTML5 \\u0111&atilde; gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u \\u0111&aacute;ng k\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eefng h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a flash k\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb khi n&oacute; l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u ra th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. HTML5 c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 cung c\\u1ea5p h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th&iacute;ch t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n cho nhi\\u1ec1u tr&igrave;nh duy\\u1ec7t h\\u01a1n tr&ecirc;n c\\u1ea3 m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 b&