(16,	74,	'Chief Communications Officer of Tinhvan Group represents',	'Chief Communications Officer of Tinhvan Group represents to attend the series of ICT events',	'<p>In response to the YEAR OF NATIONAL DIGITAL TRANSFORMATION, and at the same time contributing to the development of the force of digital technology startups, VINASA cooperates with the Office of the Scheme of &ldquo;Supporting the national innovation startup ecosystem by 2025&rdquo; (Scheme 844) to organize a series of events to promote digital technology startups in the framework of National Techfest 2020.</p>\n\n<p>In the framework of the event, on November 26, 2020, The Vietnam Digital Investor Club (VDI) was officially launched. This is the first club specialized in digital start-up investment in Vietnam, bringing together investors, entrepreneurs and large corporations and technology investment funds.</p>\n\n<p>VDI will focus on 5 main activities: (1) Startup network development, consultancy and investment for Startup, (2) Professional training on startup investment for members, (3) Exchange and sharing of investment experience, (4) Regular activities include: Start-up Caf&eacute; held once a month, Investment Conference every 6 months, (5) Research on establishing a Professional Investment Fund (With an orientation to 2022).</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-05-27 14:46:05',	'2021-06-11 12:52:42',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
