(110,	117,	'Tinhvan SoftWare  The Breakthrough in Quality',	'With the aim to improve the quality of its human resources and production as well as to enhance the competitiveness to meet the demand of clients from Japan  strategic market of Tinhvan SoftWare JSC. (TSO), the management  has approved a number of training programs. Part of it is to create favorable condition and appoint excellent personnel to participate in  international Certificate Tests in general, and certificate recognized by Japan in particular.',	'<p>With the aim to improve the quality of its human resources and production as well as to enhance the competitiveness to meet the demand of clients from Japan &ndash; strategic market of Tinhvan Software  JSC. (TSO), the management &nbsp;has approved a number of training programs. Part of it is to create favorable condition and appoint excellent personnel to participate in &nbsp;international Certificate Tests in general, and certificate recognized by Japan in particular.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recently, 33 employees from 3 locations: Hanoi, Danang, Ho Chi Minh City were chose to take part in Fundamental Engineering Test on June 24. The fact that all of test fee was covered by TSO once again reaffirmed its determination to invest in human resource and EMPLOYEE First spirit. FE Certificate is acknowledged by 7 countries of IT Professional Examination Council (ITPEC) including Japan, Philippines, Thailand, Vietnam, Myanmar, Mongolia and Bangladesh. This certificate not only partly proves the competence of company but also has the value to create new opportunities for careers of those who achieve it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Dao Quang Minh, Delivery Manager of Business Unit 2, who has attained this certificate since its first implementation in Vietnam said: &ldquo;<em>I myself consider FE has higher value than some certificates &nbsp;such as SCJP or MCSD since it includes most of basic knowledge that IT engineer need to own. It has no expiration date. TSO has been intensively developing&nbsp; Japanese market. Thus, FE Certificate can strengthen our profile as well as the whole company&rsquo;s&rdquo;</em>. Thanks to all of these reasons, since the first announcement about FE, this training drew attention of many people from Delivery Team, in which TSO Danang is a notable instance when its member actively prepared for the group study in order to increase the effectiveness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Dao Quang Minh, Delivery Manager of Business Unit 2, who has attained this certificate since its first implementation in Vietnam said: &ldquo;<em>I myself consider FE has higher value than some certificates &nbsp;such as SCJP or MCSD since it includes most of basic knowledge that IT engineer need to own. It has no expiration date. TSO has been intensively developing&nbsp; Japanese market. Thus, FE Certificate can strengthen our profile as well as the whole company&rsquo;s&rdquo;</em>. Thanks to all of these reasons, since the first announcement about FE, this training drew attention of many people from Delivery Team, in which TSO Danang is a notable instance when its member actively prepared for the group study in order to increase the effectiveness.</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-06-11 13:15:50',	'2021-06-11 13:15:50',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
