(122,	122,	'TSO sponsored Vietnam IT Day 2016 in Tokyo',	'TSOs COO and BU2s MD & Deputy Director Appointment  Ceremony was held at Tinhvan Group on May 16, 2016 with the witness of all of Tinhvan Groups Board of Directors.',	'<p>In order to promote the co-operation between Vietnam and Japan enterprises, Vietnam Software and IT Service Association (Vinasa) and Vietnam &ndash; Japan IT Cooperation Club (VJC) had successfully organized Vietnam IT Day 2016 in Tokyo, Japan with the theme of &ldquo;Vietnam Japan IT Cooperation heading to TPP&rdquo;. Tinhvan Software Joint Stock Company was one of the main sponsors for this event.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vietnam IT Day 2016 had attracted the attention of many domestic enterprises even in the very first day of the event. There were more than 200 Japan enterprises attended the event, with 16 units from Vietnam which all are leading IT names nationwide. This was not only the chance for Vietnam IT enterprise to raise the image and position but also to prove their delivery capacity toward Japan partners.<br />\r\nAt the event, CEO of Tinhvan Software cum Vice President of VJC Nguyen Ich Vinh had a speech on the role of Japan in TPP and both opportunities and challenges for Vietnam IT Outsourcing companies. Through the speech, he also states that in the concept of TPP Agreement being signed, along with the applied policies with favorable toward Outsourcing of Japanese government, Vietnam enterprises, in which including Tinhvan Software, are standing in front of the opportunity to develop comprehensively into Japan market. With the establishment of Tinhvan Software Japan in November 2015, Tinhvan Software once again re-claim Japan as the strategic market of TSO. Tinhvan Software is striving their best to stand side by side, to support customers more efficiently, toward a long-term and developing cooperating relationship.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-06-14 09:02:07',	'2021-07-07 15:37:36',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
