(125,	123,	'TSO was honored in Vietnam IT Outsourcing Excellence Award 2015',	'Ho Chi Minh City, 15 October, 2015  Within the framework of Vietnam Information Technology Development Conference organized by Quang Trung Software City and Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association',	'<p><em>Ho Chi Minh City, 15 October, 2015 &ndash; Within the framework of Vietnam Information Technology Development Conference organized by Quang Trung Software City and Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association, Tinhvan Software JSC was honored with the title of Vietnam IT Outsourcing Excellence Award 2015 (VNITO Award 2015). The award presents the recognition as well as high remark of the leading experts and organizations for Tinhvan Software.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to recognize and honor ITO/BPO enterprises achieving outstanding business results in Vietnam, the &ldquo;<em>Vietnam IT Outsourcing Excellence Award</em>&rdquo; was held for the first time in Vietnam with the award council consisting of leading experts from prestigious organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After many weeks of careful evaluation, Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association (HCA) announced 33 enterprises to be awarded. With the achievements as well as the outstanding growth, Tinhvan Software has&nbsp;excellently been named to be one of the Vietnam leading IT outsourcing enterprises for 2015. This event is a milestone on the process of development of Tinhvan SoftWare and is also a worthy recognition by leading experts and organizations for the continuous effort of TSO.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tinhvan Software has made a stronger and stronger impression on not only the partners but also the experts and the enterprises of the same industry by our professional and serious investment. Right before attending the Vietnam IT Outsourcing Development Conference (Vietnam ITO Conference 2015), CEO of Tinhvan Software cum Vice President of Vietnam &ndash; Japan IT Cooperation Club (VJC) Nguyen Ich Vinh had a presentation on the topic &ldquo;<em>The future of Automotive Industry and Smart Transportation with IoT trend; A Case Study by Tinhvan</em>&rdquo; on 14th&nbsp;October 2015 in Japan ICT Day 2015, titled &ldquo;Collaboration on Internet of Things Applications for Social Infrastructure and Offshore Business&rdquo; jointly organized by the Association of Vietnam Software and IT Services Association (VINASA) and Vietnam &ndash; Japan IT Cooperation Club (VJC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-06-14 09:05:41',	'2021-07-05 16:17:34',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
