(144,	131,	'Sales Tracking Solution',	'The client is one of the worlds largest consumer goods companies which is stablished over 100 years ago. They are known for great brands, a global footprint and belief in doing business the right way.',	'<p><strong>The Client</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The client is one of the world&rsquo;s largest consumer goods companies which is stablished over 100 years ago. They are known for great brands, a global footprint and belief in doing business the right way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business needs</strong>: In order to track and manage the performance of their sales team across the Asia, client wants a comprehensive mobile application which is used by their salesmen to present the products, record the sales volume &amp; manage customers. The data from multiple countries is then centralized to a role-based portal for analytic purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This large-scaled solution has been developed by Tinhvan Software for 5 years and ongoing. It is rolled out in more than 20 countries globally with over 2,000 active users (which are salesmen &amp; sales leaders). Sales Tracker Solution is regarded one of the most successful projects TSO has been working on - receiving lots of credits from the client &amp; their users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Solutions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TSO built up a team the team consists in 5 R&amp;D developers based in our headquarter. We work closely with the Client Service Team and the Infrastructure team to offer tech support and maintenance when needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For salesman:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Self-manage quota &amp; KPI</li>\r\n	<li>Customers Management</li>\r\n	<li>Product presentation and Ordering</li>\r\n	<li>Data synchronization</li>\r\n	<li>Analysis report</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For sales leader:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Set/approve/manage sales target/quota/plan</li>\r\n	<li>Analysis team reports</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For CMS - a Role-based multi-country portal:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Analysis Customer management</li>\r\n	<li>Sales performance tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Product management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Project Summary</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sales information management</li>\r\n	<li>Performance Infographic</li>\r\n	<li>Application Development both Front-end &amp; Back-end</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain and update the application up to now</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Technologies Used</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>iOS, Android, PHP, .Net, Restful API, Bootstrap</p>',	'ja',	1,	'2021-07-07 19:47:05',	'2021-07-07 19:47:05',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
(145,	132,	'Large-scale Mall\'s Branches Management App',	'The client is a specialist shopping mall developer which efforts to create malls that enhance the quality of life, stimulate local economic activity and contribute to community life and culture.',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Client</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The client is a specialist shopping mall developer which efforts to create malls that enhance the quality of life, stimulate local economic activity and contribute to community life and culture.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The client wants to develop a Loyalty mobile app system to increase the engagement with consumers and encourage them to come over for shopping. Besides, transforming the marketing way from pager stuffs such as voucher, mailer to e-voucher and e-mailer helps reducing printing cost and paper use, therefore increasing the effectiveness of their marketing programs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Project Summary</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Develop a new application (client &amp; server) including UI &amp; backend/frontend.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Upgrade, maintain &amp; support for 2 years and ongoing.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Peaked traffic: 3500 rpm; 3000 CCU</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Technologies used</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">PHP, OpenCart, iOS, Android.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2021-07-07 19:54:19',	'2022-06-28 13:27:44',	'large-scale-mall-s-branches-management-app',	'Large-scale Mall\'s Branches Management App',	'Meta Keywords',	'Meta Description',	'Meta Open Graph URL'),
