(148,	133,	'Device Usage Remote Control Apps',	'A parental control app for parents to take the lead in remotely managing their children\'s screen time and device usage with just a few clicks.',	'<p><img alt=\"Device Usage Remote Control Apps\" src=\"/storage/files/Parental Control App.webp\" style=\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>The Client</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The client is a Media company in Singapore which has been a long-term partner of TSO since 2013. This is among the best projects that we have done together.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The project is a parental control app for parents to take the lead in remotely managing their children&#39;s screen time and device usage with just a few clicks. The Client wants to develop a mobile application with both iOS &amp; Android version in a certain period of time in order to fit their launching campaign in Singaporean market.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Project Summary</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Mobile development for client&#39;s application.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Maintain &amp; Update the application up to now.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Features&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Set up multiple schedules to limit device usage during school, meal times, family time, bedtime</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Block or enable children&rsquo;s access to apps like games and social media</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Enable children&rsquo;s access to other apps like educational puzzles</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2021-07-07 20:00:05',	'2022-07-28 10: