(175,	144,	'Tinhvan participates in TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021',	'Tinhvan participates in TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021',	'<p>Recently, on Sunday, June 6, 2021, the Organizing Committee of the TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises Program 2021 attended the presentation of Tinhvan Technology Joint Stock Company. This year Tinhvan participates in this Program in the category of Top 10 Enterprises providing Digital Government solutions. The Voting Council consists of representatives from the Ministry of Information and Communications, leaders of the Vietnam Software and IT Services Association (VINASA), and experts in the ICT field. During the presentation, on behalf of Tinhvan Group, Communications Director Phan Quang Minh presented an overview of Tinhvan Group and Tinhvan&#39;s achievements in implementing e-Government solutions. . The Voting Council heard and highly appreciated the software solutions that Tinhvan has deployed to ministry, branches, and localities, typically the Ministry of Finance, the State Securities Commission, and the Radio Frequency Department. &hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enterprises participating in the poll will be evaluated according to 7 criteria including financial indicators, human and human resources, products, technological capabilities, management, achievements, and additional criteria. industry-specific assessments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The evaluation process consists of 3 rounds including Pre-qualification of dossiers; Presentation and Practical Appraisal; and General Selection. The evaluation council is the experts in the fields of technology, finance, administration, e-commerce, and Startup, the leading prestigious specialized reporter in Vietnam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The announcement and certification ceremony of the TOP 10 Vietnamese IT enterprises in 2021 is expected to be held on July 13, ahead of the Vietnam ICT Summit 2021.</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:27:52',	'2022-06-28 16:52:34',	'tinhvan-participates-in-top-10-vietnam-it-enterprises-2021',	'Tinhvan Participates In TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021',	'Tinhvan Participates In TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021',	'Tinhvan Participates In TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021',	'Tinhvan Participates In TOP 10 Vietnam IT Enterprises 2021'),
(176,	144,	'Tinh Vn tham d Chng trnh TOP 10 Doanh nghip CNTT Vit Nam 2021',	'Tinh Vn tham d Chng trnh TOP 10 Doanh nghip CNTT Vit Nam 2021',	'<p>Va qua, v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y Ch Nht, 6/6/2021, Ban t chc Chng tr&igrave;nh TOP 10 Doanh nghip CNTT Vit Nam 2021 &atilde; d bui thuyt tr&igrave;nh ca C&ocirc;ng ty C phn C&ocirc;ng ngh Tinh V&acirc;n. Nm nay Tinh V&acirc;n tham gia v&agrave;o Chng tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y  hng mc Top 10 Doanh nghip cung cp gii ph&aacute;p Ch&iacute;nh ph s. Hi ng B&igrave;nh chn gm c&aacute;c i din n t B Th&ocirc;ng tin truyn th&ocirc;ng, l&atilde;nh o Hip hi Phn mm v&agrave; Dch v CNTT Vit Nam (VINASA) v&agrave; c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia trong lnh vc ICT. Trong bui thuyt tr&igrave;nh, thay mt cho Tinhvan Group, Gi&aacute;m c Truyn th&ocirc;ng Phan Quang Minh &atilde; tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y, gii thiu tng quan v Tinhvan Group, v c&aacute;c kt qu t c ca Tinh V&acirc;n trong vic trin khai c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p Ch&iacute;nh ph in t. Hi ng B&igrave;nh chn &atilde; nghe v&agrave; &aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao nhng gii ph&aacute;p phn mm m&agrave; Tinh V&acirc;n &atilde; trin khai cho c&aacute;c B, ng&agrave;nh, a phng, ti&ecirc;u biu nh B T&agrave;i Ch&iacute;nh, U ban Chng kho&aacute;n Nh&agrave; nc, Cc Tn s v&ocirc; tuyn in &hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c doanh nghip tham gia b&igrave;nh chn s c &aacute;nh gi&aacute; theo 7 ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; gm: Ch ti&ecirc;u t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&acirc;n lc nh&acirc;n s, sn phm, nng lc c&ocirc;ng ngh, c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qun tr, th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch &atilde; t c v&agrave; c&oacute; th&ecirc;m ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; &aacute;nh gi&aacute; c th&ugrave; ri&ecirc;ng theo ng&agrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quy tr&igrave;nh &aacute;nh gi&aacute; gm 03 v&ograve;ng bao gm: S tuyn h s; Thuyt tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; Thm nh thc t; v&agrave; B&igrave;nh chn chung tuyn. Hi ng &aacute;nh gi&aacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia trong lnh vc c&ocirc;ng ngh, t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh, qun tr, thng mi in t, Startup, ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh uy t&iacute;n h&agrave;ng u Vit Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L c&ocirc;ng b v&agrave; Trao chng nhn TOP 10 DN CNTT Vit Nam 2021 d kin s c t chc ng&agrave;y 13/7, trc thm Din &agrave;n Cp cao CNTT &ndash; TT Vit Nam 2021.</p>',	'vi',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:27:52',	'2021-07-16 10:27:52',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
