(187,	148,	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'<p><img alt=\"Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021\" src=\"/storage/files/News/Events/Tinh Van Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The year 2021 marks a big change for Tinhvan Software. The company changed its name from Tinhvan Software (TSO), a key unit in Tinhvan Group&#39;s Go Global strategy, to Tinhvan Software (TSO) not only providing Outsourcing services but also expanding its business activities in products digital transformation products and solutions for businesses with the Biz@DX solution suite.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In 2015, Tinhvan Software received the title of Vietnam&#39;s Leading IT Outsourcing Enterprise 2015 by the Ho Chi Minh City Computer Association.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This year, Tinhvan Software was awarded Sao Khue Award in the field of software export services. This is the recognition of the BTC (Vinasa) as well as of the Vietnamese IT community for Tinhvan Software&#39;s contributions in the field of software outsourcing and exporting in recent years.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sao Khue Award is the most prestigious award in the field of software and IT services, held since 2003, accompanying the history of establishment and development of the Vietnam Association of Software and IT Services Enterprises. Vinasa and sponsored by the Ministry of Information and Communications.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This event was also reported by many prestigious newspapers such as VTV, Thanh Nien, etc., to congratulate Tinhvan Software for our efforts to achieve this accomplishment</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-trong-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-post1452002.html</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">https://vtv.vn/cong-nghe/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2022-linh-vuc-dich-vu-xuat-khau-phan-mem-20220423155230865.htm</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em>Photo: Mr. Bui Thanh Tung, director of BU2 - Tinhvan Software - received the Sao Khue 2022 award.</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'en',	1,	'2021-07-16 10:35:30',	'2022-07-28 14:20:17',	'tinhvan-software-received-the-sao-khue-award-2022-for-best-software-outsourcing-service-2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'Tinhvan Software Received The Sao Khue Award 2022 For Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021'),
(188,	148,	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021 Vn',	'Tinhvan Software received the Sao Khue Award 2022 for Best Software Outsourcing Service 2021',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nm 2021 &aacute;nh du mt s thay i ln ca Tinhvan Software. C&ocirc;ng ty i t&ecirc;n t Tinhvan Software (TSO), n v ch lc trong chin lc Go Global ca Tinhvan Group, th&agrave;nh Tinhvan Software (TSO) kh&ocirc;ng ch cung cp dch v Gia c&ocirc;ng m&agrave; c&ograve;n m rng hot ng kinh doanh  c&aacute;c sn phm v&agrave; gii ph&aacute;p chuyn i s cho doanh nghip vi B gii ph&aacute;p Biz @ DX.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nm 2015, <strong>Tinhvan Software </strong>nhn danh hiu <strong><em>Doanh nghip Gia c&ocirc;ng CNTT </em></strong>H&agrave;ng u Vit Nam 2015 do Hi Tin hc TP.HCM trao tng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nm nay, <strong>Tinhvan Software</strong> &atilde; c trao gii Sao Khu&ecirc; trong lnh vc dch v xut khu phn mm. &acirc;y l&agrave; s ghi nhn ca BTC (Vinasa) cng nh ca cng ng CNTT Vit Nam i vi nhng &oacute;ng g&oacute;p ca Tinhvan Software trong lnh vc gia c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; xut khu phn mm trong thi gian qua.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong>Gii thng Sao Khu&ecirc;</strong></em> l&agrave; gii thng uy t&iacute;n nht trong lnh vc phn mm v&agrave; dch v CNTT, c t chc t nm 2003, ng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng lch s h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin ca Hip hi Doanh nghip phn mm v&agrave; dch v CNTT Vit Nam. Vinasa v&agrave; c s bo tr ca B Th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; Truyn th&ocirc;ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">S kin n&agrave;y cng c nhiu trang b&aacute;o uy t&iacute;n nh b&aacute;o VTV, B&aacute;o Thanh Ni&ecirc;n,&hellip; a tin v&agrave; ch&uacute;c mng cho nhng n lc ca Tinhvan Software  t c th&agrave;nh tu n&agrave;y.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tinhvan-software-nhan-giai-thuong-sao-khue-2