(456,	208,	'Deploying health check for Tinhvaners',	'Deploying health check for Tinhvaners',	'<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In the context of the complicated situation of the<em><strong> COVID-19</strong></em> epidemic across the country, it is extremely necessary to vaccinate people against Covid-19 to create herd immunity. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Understanding this, from the end of July, <strong>Tinhvan Group</strong> organized the 1st injection for staff and completed the 2nd injection on September 23. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">After this injection, 99% of the staff at <strong>Tinhvan Group</strong> have completed the 1st injection and 90% have fully injected 2 doses of the vaccine, fulfilling the civic responsibility in creating community immunity, helping each person to work with complete peace of mind.<br />\r\nThis is possible thanks to the right and timely policy, the attention of the <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">Board of Directors and the Company&#39;s Covid Prevention Steering Committee</span>, the urgency and dedication of the Human Resources Department, in order to ensure the health and safety. of Tinhvaners during this epidemic season.<br />\r\nHopefully with these favorable conditions Tinhvaners will be strong and healthy to overcome the pandemic and at the same time seize opportunities in the new context, creating a breakthrough in the coming time.</span></span></p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-05-31 14:22:03',	'2022-07-26 16:30:11',	'deploying-health-check-for-tinhvaners',	'Deploying Health Check For Tinhvaners',	'Deploying Health Check For Tinhvaners',	'Deploying Health Check For Tinhvaners',	'Deploying Health Check For Tinhvaners'),
