ute;c y doanh s b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng ca h. Nhng Thrasio &atilde; phi i mt vi nhng kh&oacute; khn ca ri&ecirc;ng m&igrave;nh gn &acirc;y, th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o sa thi &aacute;ng k v&agrave; thay i Gi&aacute;m c iu h&agrave;nh ln th hai trong t&aacute;m th&aacute;ng. Mt s nh&agrave; quan s&aacute;t ng&agrave;nh thng mi in t &atilde; bt u t c&acirc;u hi v vic liu m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh kinh doanh Amazon-rollup c&oacute; bn vng hay kh&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi &oacute;, c&aacute;c t tng hp Shopify-seller vn c&oacute; v hp dn i vi c&aacute;c nh&agrave; u t: OpenStore.</p>',	'vi',	1,	'2022-06-09 15:39:43',	'2022-06-09 15:39:43',	'shopify-app-aggregators-spendings-millions-to-acquire-apps-2022',	'Cc cty ln ang mua li cc doanh nghip  t c thnh cng trn Shopify App Store',	'Shopify, e-commerce',	'Nhng ngi sng to ng dng Shopify ang kim tin bng cc giao dch hng triu  la trong khi cc cng ty c ti tr tt bt u trn ngp khng gian  tm kim cc thng v mua li.',	'https://www.businessinsider.com/shopify-app-aggregators-spendings-millions-to-acquire-apps-2022-6'),
