(622,	267,	'Salesforce officially unveils its software to help companies make and manage NFTs, months after employees protested against its plans to enter crypto',	'Salesforce debuted a pilot of NFT Cloud, helping its customers create and manage NFTs.',	'<p>Salesforce has debuted the first version of its NFT Cloud, a product to help its corporate clients create and manage non-fungible tokens (NFTs), the company announced Wednesday.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NFT Cloud, the company&#39;s first entrance into the so-called Web3 market of cryptocurrency-related technologies, will be part of the company&#39;s Commerce Cloud suite. As of Wednesday,&nbsp;the NFT Cloud is only available in a closed pilot, as select customers test it out.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;This is all about helping our customers deliver connected and personalized experience across both the physical and the digital world,&quot; Adam Caplan, Salesforce senior VP of Emerging Technology, said at a press conference earlier this week. &quot;So NFT cloud, it&#39;s all about helping our customers mint, manage and sell NFTs.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Caplan said the new product was the result of conversations with customers who asked Salesforce to help them &quot;navigate Web3.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Salesforce&#39;s plans to build NFT Cloud were&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2022/02/09/salesforce-tells-employees-its-working-on-nft-cloud-service.html\">first reported by CNBC&nbsp;</a>in February. In the wake of that report, over 400 employees signed on to an open letter to co-CEOs Marc Benioff and Bret Taylor in protest, citing the environmental and economic impact of NFTs,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://news.trust.org/item/20220218170402-ug6bk/\">Thomson Reuters Foundation News first reported.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;We are grateful to have a culture where employees are empowered to voice their opinions. We are holding listening sessions with interested employees and will incorporate their feedback in our path forward,&quot; a Salesforce spokesperson told Insider amid the backlash in February.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While the NFT and larger cryptocurrency markets have grown tremendously in recent years, they have also proven controversial in the tech industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the letter, the Salesforce employees argued that building an NFT product would be a de facto endorsement of an unregulated industry that has seen many people lose their savings and livelihoods via risky investments and scams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They also said that the carbon emissions that come with NFTs are at odds with Salesforce&#39;s own pro-environmental messaging &mdash; including in its Super Bowl ad in February, which starred actor Matthew McConaughey. The company also announced earlier this year that it would&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/salesforce-executive-salaries-diversity-inclusion-goals-marc-benioff-2022-2\">tie executive pay to certain sustainability goals</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The NFT Cloud product announced today is built with &quot;sustainability at its core,&quot; Caplan said. That means Salesforce is providing customers with more sustainable blockchain options, automating carbon emission calculations, and letting brands offset emissions by purchasing carbon credits, he said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When asked about the sentiment that NFTs are a passing fad as the market for them cools off, Caplan said they are not focusing on the value of the NFTs themselves but rather on the potential that the technology could be useful for customers. Caplan also said that Salesforce is building security features into NFT Cloud, in response to the spate of scams that have hit users in the space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to NFTs, Caplan said customers are asking for ways to use blockchain technology to track ethical sourcing in supply chains and collecting data from their online customers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;We&#39;re learning as we go, obviously,&quot; Caplan said. &quot;And it&#39;s a long road to see how this all evolves.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Do you work at Salesforce?</strong>&nbsp;Contact this reporter via email at pzaveri@insider.com or Signal at 925-364-4258. (PR pitches by email only, please.)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Source:&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>https://www.businessinsider.com/salesforce-nft-cloud-web3-cryptocurrency-management-software-2022-6</em></p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-09 16:00:25',	'2022-06-28 16:28:14',	'salesforce-nft-cloud-web3-cryptocurrency-management-software-2022',	'Salesforce Officially Unveils Its Software To Help Companies Make And Manage NFTs, Months After Employees Protested Against Its Plans To Enter Crypto',	'Salesforce, NFT, blockchain',	'Salesforce debuted a pilot of NFT Cloud, helping its customers create and manage NFTs.',	'https://www.businessinsider.com/salesforce-nft-cloud-web3-cryptocurrency-management-software-2022-6'),
(623,	267,	'Salesforce chnh thc tit l phn mm ca mnh  gip cc cng ty to v qun l NFT, vi thng sau khi nhn vin phn i k hoch thm nhp tin in t',	'Salesforce  ra mt bn th nghim ca NFT Cloud, gip khch hng ca mnh to v qun l cc NFT.\r\nMt s nhn vin ca Salesforce trc y  phn i  tng ny, vi l do lo ngi v mi trng v kinh t.',	'<p>Salesforce &atilde; ra mt phi&ecirc;n bn u ti&ecirc;n ca NFT Cloud, mt sn phm  gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng doanh nghip ca m&igrave;nh to v&agrave; qun l&yacute; c&aacute;c m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng th thay th (NFT), c&ocirc;ng ty &atilde; c&ocirc;ng b h&ocirc;m th T.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NFT Cloud, li v&agrave;o u ti&ecirc;n ca c&ocirc;ng ty v&agrave;o c&aacute;i gi l&agrave; th trng Web3 ca c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh li&ecirc;n quan n tin in t, s l&agrave; mt phn ca b Commerce Cloud ca c&ocirc;ng ty. K t th T, NFT Cloud ch c&oacute; sn trong mt th nghim k&iacute;n, khi mt s kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c chn th nghim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adam Caplan, Ph&oacute; ch tch cp cao ca Salesforce v C&ocirc;ng ngh mi ni, cho bit trong mt cuc hp b&aacute;o u tun n&agrave;y: &ldquo;Tt c iu n&agrave;y l&agrave; nhm gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i mang li tri nghim c kt ni v&agrave; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n h&oacute;a tr&ecirc;n c th gii vt l&yacute; v&agrave; k thut s. &quot;V&igrave; vy, &aacute;m m&acirc;y NFT, tt c ch nhm gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &uacute;c, qun l&yacute; v&agrave; b&aacute;n NFT.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Caplan cho bit sn phm mi l&agrave; kt qu ca c&aacute;c cuc tr&ograve; chuyn vi nhng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng y&ecirc;u cu Salesforce gi&uacute;p h &quot;iu hng Web3.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>K hoch x&acirc;y dng NFT Cloud ca Salesforce ln u ti&ecirc;n c CNBC b&aacute;o c&aacute;o v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng Hai. Sau b&aacute;o c&aacute;o &oacute;, hn 400 nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &atilde; k&yacute; v&agrave;o mt bc th ng gi cho c&aacute;c ng CEO Marc Benioff v&agrave; Bret Taylor  phn i, tr&iacute;ch dn t&aacute;c ng m&ocirc;i trng v&agrave; kinh t ca NFT, Thomson Reuters Foundation News a tin u ti&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngi ph&aacute;t ng&ocirc;n ca Salesforce n&oacute;i vi Insider rng: &quot;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i rt bit n v&igrave; c&oacute; mt nn vn h&oacute;a ni nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c trao quyn  n&oacute;i l&ecirc;n &yacute; kin ca h. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ang t chc c&aacute;c bui lng nghe vi nhng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n quan t&acirc;m v&agrave; s kt hp phn hi ca h trong con ng tin l&ecirc;n ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi NFT v&agrave; c&aacute;c th trng tin in t ln hn &atilde; ph&aacute;t trin rt nhiu trong nhng nm gn &acirc;y, ch&uacute;ng cng &atilde; g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i trong ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ngh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong th, c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ca Salesforce lp lun rng vic x&acirc;y dng mt sn phm NFT s l&agrave; s chng thc tr&ecirc;n thc t i vi mt ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghip kh&ocirc;ng c kim so&aacute;t &atilde; chng kin nhiu ngi mt tin tit kim v&agrave; sinh k do c&aacute;c khon u t mo him v&agrave; la o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H cng n&oacute;i rng lng kh&iacute; thi carbon i k&egrave;m vi NFTs tr&aacute;i ngc vi th&ocirc;ng ip ng h m&ocirc;i trng ca ch&iacute;nh Salesforce - bao gm c trong qung c&aacute;o Super Bowl v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 2, c&oacute; s tham gia ca nam din vi&ecirc;n Matthew McConaughey. C&ocirc;ng ty cng &atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v&agrave;o u nm nay rng h s buc tr lng cho gi&aacute;m c iu h&agrave;nh vi c&aacute;c mc ti&ecirc;u bn vng nht nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Caplan cho bit, sn phm NFT Cloud c c&ocirc;ng b ng&agrave;y h&ocirc;m nay c x&acirc;y dng vi &quot;t&iacute;nh bn vng l&agrave; ct l&otilde;i ca n&oacute;&quot;. iu &oacute; c&oacute; ngha l&agrave; Salesforce ang cung cp cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y chn blockchain bn vng hn, t ng h&oacute;a t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n ph&aacute;t thi carbon v&agrave; cho ph&eacute;p c&aacute;c thng hiu b&ugrave; p lng kh&iacute; thi bng c&aacute;ch mua t&iacute;n dng carbon, &ocirc;ng n&oacute;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi c hi v cm gi&aacute;c rng NFTs ang l&agrave; mt nht thi khi th trng d&agrave;nh cho ch&uacute;ng ngui i, Caplan cho bit h kh&ocirc;ng tp trung v&agrave;o gi&aacute; tr ca bn th&acirc;n NFT m&agrave; thay v&agrave;o &oacute; l&agrave; tim nng m&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ngh n&agrave;y c&oacute; th hu &iacute;ch cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng. Caplan cng n&oacute;i rng Salesforce ang x&acirc;y dng c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng bo mt v&agrave;o NFT Cloud,  i ph&oacute; vi h&agrave;ng lot c&aacute;c tr&ograve; gian ln &atilde; tn c&ocirc;ng ngi d&ugrave;ng trong kh&ocirc;ng gian.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i NFTs, Caplan cho bit kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ang y&ecirc;u cu c&aacute;c c&aacute;ch s dng c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain  theo d&otilde;i ngun cung ng c&oacute; o c trong chui cung ng v&agrave; thu thp d liu t kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trc tuyn ca h.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;R&otilde; r&agrave;ng l&agrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ang hc khi ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i i,&quot; Caplan n&oacute;i. &quot;V&agrave; &oacute; l&agrave; mt con ng d&agrave;i  xem tt c iu n&agrave;y ph&aacute;t trin nh th n&agrave;o.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn c&oacute; l&agrave;m vic ti Salesforce kh&ocirc;ng? Li&ecirc;n h vi ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n n&agrave;y qua email ti pzaveri@insider.com hoc Signal theo s 925-364-4258. (Vui l&ograve;ng ch qung c&aacute;o chi&ecirc;u h&agrave;ng qua email.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Source:&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>https://www.businessinsider.com/salesforce-nft-cloud-web3-cryptocurrency-management-software-2022-6</em></p>',	'vi',	1,	'2022-06-09 16:00:25',	'2022-06-09 16:06:12',	'salesforce-nft-cloud-web3-cryptocurrency-management-software-2022',	'Salesforce chnh thc tit l phn mm ca mnh  gip cc cng ty to v qun l NFT, vi thng sau khi nhn vin phn i k hoch thm nhp tin in t',	'Salesforce, NFT, blockchain',	'Salesforce  ra mt bn th nghim ca NFT Cloud, gip khch hng ca mnh to v qun l cc NFT. 