(625,	268,	'Ousted WeWork founder Adam Neumann wants to put carbon credits on the blockchain with \'goddess nature tokens\' to combat climate change',	'Ex-WeWork CEO Adam Neumann and his wife are launching a new startup called Flowcarbon.\r\nThe project aims to use the blockchain to let businesses trade carbon credits using crypto tokens.\r\nThose tokens have been dubbed Goddess Nature Tokens, or GNTs.',	'<p>Carbon trading is getting the crypto treatment, and its latest orchestrator is none other than WeWork&#39;s eccentric cofounder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Three years after being ousted as CEO,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/wework-ceo-adam-neumann-bio-life-career-2019-8\">Adam Neumann</a>&nbsp;is launching a new startup called&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flowcarbon.com/\">Flowcarbon</a>&nbsp;that wants to put carbon credits on blockchain technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>His idea &mdash; powered in part by a $32 million round of funding from famed Silicon Valley venture firm Andreessen Horowitz &mdash; is to make these carbon credits more accessible and easier to trade with the help of the company&#39;s flagship product: the Goddess Nature Token (GNT.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Businesses and individuals will be able to use these tokens &mdash;&nbsp; each backed by a real-life carbon credit &mdash; to buy and sell the permits on the blockchain in a decentralized manner, making the opaque and controversial process more transparent.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new endeavor marks not only a turning point for Neumann following his fall from grace but also another high-profile tech founder leaping headfirst into the booming Web3 sphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Carbon trading, otherwise known as the voluntary carbon market, is when businesses buy and sell a limited amount of government-issued permits that they can &quot;cash in&quot; when they emit carbon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The idea was to create scarcity in how much carbon the business world can emit. There are economic incentives in doing so &mdash; if a corporation doesn&#39;t use all of its carbon credits, it can sell them to peers. Depending on the country, if it emits too much carbon, it may have to buy more credits.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Neumann, per the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flowcarbon.com/\">website</a>, believes this process is flawed, built on an &quot;opaque and fractured market infrastructure&quot; with credits that have little accessibility and brokers charging sky-high fees. That&#39;s where Flowcarbon and GNTs come in.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Flowcarbon did not immediately respond to Insider&#39;s request for comment, but a spokesperson told&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vox.com/recode/23142106/adam-neumann-crypto-carbon-credit-offset-flowcarbon\">Vox</a>&nbsp;that the credits represented by the company&#39;s tokens are issued from one of four major carbon credit registries.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Flowcarbon and it&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AriannaSimpson/status/1529072554639511554?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1529072555667116032%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es2_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Fwework-founder-reinvents-himself-with-70m-crypto-carbon-credit-platform\">and its backers</a>, the blockchain is the perfect environment for trading carbon credits, given the technology&#39;s innate transparency.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Source:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://www.businessinsider.com/wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022-6</p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-09 16:20:35',	'2022-06-28 16:27:57',	'wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022',	'Ousted WeWork Founder Adam Neumann Wants To Put Carbon Credits On The Blockchain With \'goddess Nature Tokens\' To Combat Climate Change',	'Blockchain, WeWork, tokens',	'Ex-WeWork CEO Adam Neumann and his wife are launching a new startup called Flowcarbon. The project aims to use the blockchain to let businesses trade carbon credits using crypto tokens. Those tokens have been dubbed Goddess Nature Tokens, or GNTs.',	'https://www.businessinsider.com/wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022-6'),
(626,	268,	'Ngi sng lp WeWork b lt  Adam Neumann mun a cc khon tn dng carbon vo blockchain vi \'m thng bo thin nhin ca n thn\'  chng li bin i kh hu',	'Gim c iu hnh ca Ex-WeWork, Adam Neumann v v ang thnh lp mt cng ty khi nghip mi c tn Flowcarbon.\r\nD n nhm mc ch s dng blockchain  cho php cc doanh nghip giao dch tn dng carbon bng cch s dng m thng bo tin in t.\r\nNhng m thng bo  c gi l M thng bo Thin nhin N thn, hoc GNTs.',	'<p>Giao dch carbon ang c x l&yacute; bng tin in t v&agrave; ngi iu phi mi nht ca n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ai kh&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; ngi ng s&aacute;ng lp lp d ca WeWork.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ba nm sau khi b lt  khi v tr&iacute; Gi&aacute;m c iu h&agrave;nh, Adam Neumann ang khi ng mt c&ocirc;ng ty khi nghip mi c&oacute; t&ecirc;n Flowcarbon mun a t&iacute;n ch carbon v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&Yacute; tng ca &ocirc;ng - c h tr mt phn bi v&ograve;ng t&agrave;i tr 32 triu &ocirc; la t c&ocirc;ng ty mo him Andreessen Horowitz ni ting  Thung lng Silicon - l&agrave; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c khon t&iacute;n dng carbon n&agrave;y tr n&ecirc;n d tip cn hn v&agrave; giao dch d d&agrave;ng hn vi s tr gi&uacute;p ca sn phm h&agrave;ng u ca c&ocirc;ng ty: Goddess Nature Token (GNT. )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c doanh nghip v&agrave; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n s c&oacute; th s dng c&aacute;c m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o n&agrave;y - mi m&atilde; c h tr bi t&iacute;n dng carbon trong i thc -  mua v&agrave; b&aacute;n c&aacute;c giy ph&eacute;p tr&ecirc;n blockchain theo c&aacute;ch phi tp trung, l&agrave;m cho quy tr&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng v&agrave; g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i tr n&ecirc;n minh bch hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N lc mi kh&ocirc;ng ch &aacute;nh du mt bc ngot i vi Neumann sau khi anh ri v&agrave;o li t&igrave;nh m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave; mt nh&agrave; s&aacute;ng lp c&ocirc;ng ngh ni ting kh&aacute;c cng bc u bc v&agrave;o lnh vc Web3 ang b&ugrave;ng n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kinh doanh carbon, hay c&ograve;n c gi l&agrave; th trng carbon t nguyn, l&agrave; khi c&aacute;c doanh nghip mua v&agrave; b&aacute;n mt s lng hn ch giy ph&eacute;p do ch&iacute;nh ph cp m&agrave; h c&oacute; th &quot;kim c tin&quot; khi ph&aacute;t thi carbon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&Yacute; tng l&agrave; to ra s khan him v lng carbon m&agrave; th gii kinh doanh c&oacute; th thi ra. C&oacute; nhng ng lc kinh t khi l&agrave;m nh vy - nu mt c&ocirc;ng ty kh&ocirc;ng s dng tt c c&aacute;c khon t&iacute;n dng carbon ca m&igrave;nh, n&oacute; c&oacute; th b&aacute;n ch&uacute;ng cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty c&ugrave;ng ng&agrave;nh. T&ugrave;y thuc v&agrave;o quc gia, nu n&oacute; thi ra qu&aacute; nhiu carbon, n&oacute; c&oacute; th phi mua th&ecirc;m t&iacute;n dng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Neumann, theo trang web, tin rng quy tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y l&agrave; sai s&oacute;t, c x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n &quot;c s h tng th trng kh&ocirc;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng v&agrave; b ph&aacute; v&quot; vi c&aacute;c khon t&iacute;n dng c&oacute; &iacute;t kh nng tip cn v&agrave; c&aacute;c nh&agrave; m&ocirc;i gii t&iacute;nh ph&iacute; cao ngt ngng. &oacute; l&agrave; ni Flowcarbon v&agrave; GNTs xut hin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Flowcarbon &atilde; kh&ocirc;ng tr li ngay lp tc y&ecirc;u cu b&igrave;nh lun ca Insider, nhng mt ngi ph&aacute;t ng&ocirc;n n&oacute;i vi Vox rng c&aacute;c khon t&iacute;n dng c i din bi m&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o ca c&ocirc;ng ty c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh t mt trong bn c quan ng k&yacute; t&iacute;n dng carbon ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Flowcarbon v&agrave; n&oacute; v&agrave; nhng ngi ng h n&oacute;, blockchain l&agrave; m&ocirc;i trng ho&agrave;n ho  giao dch c&aacute;c khon t&iacute;n dng carbon, do t&iacute;nh minh bch bm sinh ca c&ocirc;ng ngh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Source:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://www.businessinsider.com/wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022-6</p>',	'vi',	1,	'2022-06-09 16:20:35',	'2022-06-09 16:30:05',	'wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022',	'Ngi Sng Lp WeWork B Lt  Adam Neumann Mun a Cc Khon Tn Dng Carbon Vo Blockchain Vi \'m Thng Bo Thin Nhin Ca N Thn\'  Chng Li Bin i Kh Hu',	'Blockchain, WeWork, tokens',	'Gim c iu hnh ca Ex-WeWork, Adam Neumann v v ang thnh lp mt cng ty khi nghip mi c tn Flowcarbon. D n nhm mc ch s dng blockchain  cho php cc doanh nghip giao dch tn dng carbon bng cch s dng m thng bo tin in t. Nhng m thng bo  c gi l M thng bo Thin nhin N thn, hoc GNTs.',	'https://www.businessinsider.com/wework-adam-neumann-startup-carbon-credits-goddess-nature-tokens-trading-2022-6'),
