gateways, e-wallets, etc.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Manage 30K SKU</span>.</li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-28 13:44:17',	'2022-07-27 17:35:11',	'large-scale-mall-s-branches-management-app',	'Large-scale Mall\'s Branches Management App',	'Large-scale Mall\'s Branches Management App',	'A Loyalty mobile app system where customers can search and buy products online from AEON. Customers can also search for events, using accumulate points for gift exchange etc.',	'Large-scale Mall\'s Branches Management App'),
