(683,	298,	'Education System Migration',	'Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5',	'<p><img alt=\"Education System Migration\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/system2\" style=\"height:50%; width:50%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Client: </strong>A trusted global innovator of IT and business services headquartered in Tokyo, help clients transform through consulting, industry solutions, business process services, IT modernization and managed services.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Business needs:&nbsp;</strong>Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Features:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">HTML5 has greatly reduced the limitations of flash ever since it was first introduced to the market. HTML5 can provide animations with better compatibility for more browsers on both desktops and mobile devices with proper use.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The adaptive features of HTML5 make everything easier when one is building websites.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Developers can easily change or update their animations without affecting other parts of their sites by properly organizing them into external files with specific instructions given by HTML tags.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">HTML5 has been built from the ground up with a faster and simpler file API than local storage in a flash.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 09:53:43',	'2022-07-29 15:30:55',	'education-system-migration',	'Education  System Migration',	'Education ; System Migration',	'Converting thousands of educational contents (K12) from Flash to HTML5',	'JP Client Flash Converter'),
