(746,	327,	'Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion',	'As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!',	'<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/storage/files/Case studies/cura.webp\" style=\"height:50%; width:50%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Why do you need Cura?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cura was designed for special benefit of users, aiming at better experiences and outcomes in medical care. Cura is the perfect replacement for messy hardcopy records, or multiple outdated forms of personal health check. This app is the reasonable transformation of health care, as technology has taken the stand over the years in many fields. Instead of loads of paper records, all information on your medical history is kept together in one easily accessible place, and as many records are kept as possible.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This app can be utilised for public use among family members, relatives, rather than just limited personal use.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">For better understanding &amp; illustration, graphing feature offers an overview of general health status, which means users can see multiple spots simultaneously, then zoom to specific ranges and identify points of interest.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Best of all, Cura allows you to share your health records with your doctors at your own discretion, enhancing interaction at an accessible convenience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Undoubtedly, your vital signs &amp; medication have never been taken such good care of so far!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">What makes users love Cura?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cura is a mobile app that empowers you to keep track of your own health records through many helpful features. Users can have access to a record of patient health stats over a period in form of charts to enable better medication response. Moreover, Cura serves as a personal reminder for medication and periodical health check. In case of emergency, finding the nearest clinic/medical services from the location may come in handy for timely treatment. Other features to better user experience includes retrieving historical readings and chart (up to 14 readings) for NEWS monitors &amp; sending historical readings through email or MMS to GP/Caregiver.</span></p>',	'ja',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:37:59',	'2022-07-22 09:04:09',	'cura-personal-healthcare-companion',	'Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion',	'Cura,Personal Healthcare Companion',	'As health service has always been of great importance, Cura provides convenient mobile access to your health information and valuable tools to help you receive proper medical care. A friendly personal health-care companion is no longer so far out of reach!',	'Cura - Personal Healthcare Companion'),
(747,	328,	'EHR - Electronic Health Record',	'Electronic Health Record (EHR) is a mobile application that enables you to keep track of your own health records for healthier lifestyle & appropriate treatment. EHR has revolutionized the way modern people take care of themselves.',	'<p><img alt=\"EHR - Electronic Health Record\" src=\"/storage/files/erth.webp\" style=\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Why do you need EHR App?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">In daily busy life, everyone is now having less time spent on personal health care, yet this remains a problem of great concern. However, it seems unnecessary to have a personal nurse/ assistant to be in charge of this task. This is now the time for EHR to do the job. There&rsquo;ll no longer be doubts as to how much money/ what kind of treatment you may receive according to insurance policies, which drug you&rsquo;re allergic to, when to have your next periodical check-up or medication intakes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Unlike most other health record applications, we know how to deal with security &amp; privacy issue by generating a unique OTP (one time password) so that you can choose your own doctor to have access to your health records through secured authentication. EHR creates a platform between doctors and patients to share a journal on check-ups, medication intakes. Best of all, EHR.sg allows you to share your health records with your doctors at your own discretion. Generating a unique OTP (one time password) via the app, doctors of your choice has access to your health records through secured authentication.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">EHR eliminates the need for profuse paper records and outdated forms &amp; replaces them with completely accurate &amp; reliable data.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">What makes users love EHR?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This mobile application allows users to see their personal health records on drug allergies, insurance policies, health issues, current medications, history &amp; upcoming check-up appointments. One time password (OTP) can be generated each time patient needs to consult a doctor via website. Within minutes of downloading the app &amp; signing in with your own account, you&rsquo;re ready to use a fully featured and certified EHR.</span></p>',	'en',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:40:03',	'2022-07-28 10:36:00',	'ehr-electronic-health-record',	'EHR - Electronic Health Record',	'EHR,Electronic Health Record',	'Electronic Health Record (EHR) is a mobile application that enables you to keep track of your own health records for healthier lifestyle & appropriate treatment. EHR has revolutionized the way modern people take care of themselves.',	'EHR - Electronic Health Record'),
(748,	328,	'EHR - H s y t in t',	'H s sc khe in t (EHR) l mt ng dng di ng cho php bn theo di h s sc khe ca chnh mnh  c li sng lnh mnh hn v iu tr thch hp. EHR  cch mng ha cch con ngi hin i chm sc bn thn.',	'<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/storage/files/erth.webp\" style=\"float:left; height:50%; margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px; width:50%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Ti sao bn cn ng dng EHR?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Trong cuc sng bn rn h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y, mi ngi ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng &iacute;t d&agrave;nh thi gian cho vic chm s&oacute;c sc khe c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, nhng &acirc;y vn l&agrave; mt vn  c nhiu ngi quan t&acirc;m. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n ch&uacute;ng ta kh&ocirc;ng cn thit phi c&oacute; mt y t&aacute; / tr l&yacute; ri&ecirc;ng  ph tr&aacute;ch c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y. &acirc;y l&agrave; thi im  EHR thc hin c&ocirc;ng vic. Bn s kh&ocirc;ng phi suy ngh v s tin / h&igrave;nh thc iu tr m&agrave; bn c&oacute; th nhn c theo ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo him, loi thuc bn b d ng, thi im kh&aacute;m sc khe nh k hoc t d&ugrave;ng thuc tip theo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Kh&ocirc;ng ging nh hu ht c&aacute;c ng dng h s sc khe kh&aacute;c, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i bit c&aacute;ch gii quyt vn  bo mt v&agrave; quyn ri&ecirc;ng t bng c&aacute;ch to mt OTP (mt khu d&ugrave;ng mt ln) duy nht  bn c&oacute; th chn b&aacute;c s ca ri&ecirc;ng m&igrave;nh, c&oacute; quyn truy cp v&agrave;o h s sc khe ca bn th&ocirc;ng qua x&aacute;c thc bo mt. EHR to ra mt nn tng gia b&aacute;c s v&agrave; bnh nh&acirc;n  chia s nht k&yacute; v qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh kim tra, s dng thuc. Hn ht, EHR.sg cho ph&eacute;p bn chia s h s sc khe ca m&igrave;nh vi b&aacute;c s theo quyt nh ca ri&ecirc;ng bn. To mt OTP duy nht (mt khu d&ugrave;ng mt ln) th&ocirc;ng qua ng dng, c&aacute;c b&aacute;c s m&agrave; bn chn c&oacute; quyn truy cp v&agrave;o h s sc khe ca bn th&ocirc;ng qua x&aacute;c thc bo mt.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">EHR loi b nhu cu v h s giy tha v&agrave; c&aacute;c biu mu li thi &amp; thay th ch&uacute;ng bng d liu ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c v&agrave; &aacute;ng tin cy.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">iu g&igrave; khin ngi d&ugrave;ng y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch EHR?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ng dng di ng n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng xem h s sc khe c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ca h v d ng thuc, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo him, c&aacute;c vn  sc khe, thuc hin ti, tin s v&agrave; c&aacute;c cuc hn kh&aacute;m sp ti. Mt khu d&ugrave;ng mt ln (OTP) c&oacute; th c to mi khi bnh nh&acirc;n cn hi &yacute; kin b&aacute;c s qua trang web. Trong v&ograve;ng v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t sau khi ti xung ng dng v&agrave; ng nhp bng t&agrave;i khon ca ri&ecirc;ng bn, bn &atilde; sn s&agrave;ng s dng EHR y  t&iacute;nh nng v&agrave; c chng nhn.</span></p>',	'vi',	1,	'2022-06-30 13:40:03',	'2022-07-21 15:49:44',	'ehr-electronic-health-record',	'EHR - H s y t in t',	'EHR,H s y t in t',	'H s sc khe in t (EHR) l mt ng dng di ng cho php bn theo di h s sc khe ca chnh mnh  c li sng lnh mnh hn v iu tr thch hp. EHR  cch mng ha cch con ngi hin i chm sc bn thn.',	'EHR - H s y t in t'),
