(816,	311,	'Paper Master',	'A mobile game app, that players could be able to participate fully through process of paper manufacture, from plan timber trees, paper production to paper distribution in offices.',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Paper Master</strong> is a mobile game app, that players could be able to participate fully through process of paper manufacture, from plan timber trees, paper production to paper distribution in offices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Immerse yourself in the process of paper making by earning your own paper resources!<br />\r\nEnjoy PaperMaster on your smartphone.<br />\r\nInvite your friends and earn 10 bonus points up to max of 50.<br />\r\nShow off your scores and achievements.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Technical detail</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Operating System/Environment:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Requires iOS 4.0 or later.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Compatible with iPhone 3GS, iPhone 4, iPhone 4S, iPhone 5, iPhone 5c, iPhone 5s, iPad, iPod touch (3rd generation), iPod touch (4th generation) and iPod touch (5th generation).</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Optimized for iPhone 5</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'ja',	1,	'2022-06-30 12:48:58',	'2022-06-30 12:48:58',	'Paper-Master',	'Paper Master',	'Paper Master',	'Paper Master is a mobile game app, that players could be able to participate fully through process of paper manufacture, from plan timber trees, paper production to paper distribution in offices.  Features',	'Paper Master'),
