(866,	353,	'S pht trin v tng lai ca Blockchain',	'Blockchain ln u tin xut hin vi t cch l Cng ngh s ci phn tn (Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT) ) h tr cc giao dch Bitcoin sm nht, do Satoshi Nakamoto thc hin.',	'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://blockchain.tso.vn/\">Blockchain</a> ln u ti&ecirc;n xut hin vi t c&aacute;ch l&agrave; C&ocirc;ng ngh s c&aacute;i ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n (Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT) ) h tr c&aacute;c giao dch Bitcoin sm nht, do Satoshi Nakamoto thc hin.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"S pht trin v tng lai ca Blockchain\" src=\"/storage/files/News/DX News/S pht trin v tng lai ca Blockchain.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gn mi s&aacute;u nm tr&ocirc;i qua, s ph&aacute;t trin ca blockchain &atilde; c&oacute; nhng bc ph&aacute;t trin nhy vt, tr th&agrave;nh nn tng ca nhiu th trng v&agrave; g&acirc;y dng c ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghip ca ri&ecirc;ng n&oacute;. S tri dy ca c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t trin blockchain  khp mi ni &atilde; chng t c tim nng ca ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ngh n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Lnh vc Crypto thng qu&aacute; tp trung v&agrave;o c&aacute;c Hype Coin nh Shiba Inu hoc ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch gi&aacute; u c. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, mt s c&aacute; nh&acirc;n - th&ocirc;ng minh nht h&agrave;nh tinh, c&oacute; nhiu gi&aacute; tr phi tp trung, kh&ocirc;ng cn cp ph&eacute;p  tr&ecirc;n nn tng m&atilde; h&oacute;a ca h - ang mun th&uacute;c y gi&aacute; tr thc v&agrave;o s ph&aacute;t trin ca Bitcoin.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Trong b&agrave;i vit n&agrave;y, ch&uacute;ng ta s tho lun v c&aacute;c blockchain Lp 1 v&agrave; Lp 2, c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t trin blockchain ln v&agrave; nhng g&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; th mong i t blockchain trong tng lai gn.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>C&aacute;c nh&agrave; l&atilde;nh o ph&aacute;t trin Blockchain</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Mc d&ugrave; hin nay c&oacute; mt s c&ocirc;ng ty chuy&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t trin Blockchain ang to ra l&agrave;n s&oacute;ng ln trong lnh vc, nhiu c&ocirc;ng ty c&ocirc;ng ngh truyn thng nh Microsoft cng ang hot ng rt t&iacute;ch cc trong lnh vc y tim nng n&agrave;y. V&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 9 nm 2021, Microsoft ch&iacute;nh thc th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o s ngng hot ng Azure blockchain ca m&igrave;nh do kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n hng th&uacute; i vi c&aacute;c sn phm Blockchain-as-a-Service (BaaS).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Microsoft &atilde; cung cp cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng hin ti ca h mt gii ph&aacute;p chuyn i th&ocirc;ng qua ConSensys.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Mt trong nhng c&ocirc;ng ty Blockchain h&agrave;ng u l&agrave; Chainalysis, mt c&ocirc;ng ty tp trung v&agrave;o vic x&acirc;y dng nim tin v&agrave;o c&aacute;c blockchain th&ocirc;ng qua d liu. Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca h kh&ocirc;ng ch Barclays, Commonwealth Bank v&agrave; Bitpay; dch v ca c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;y gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t hn 400 t &ocirc; la t&agrave;i sn tin in t mi th&aacute;ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">C&aacute;c nh&agrave; l&atilde;nh o ph&aacute;t trin Blockchain kh&aacute;c ang nhanh ch&oacute;ng t&igrave;m ra c&aacute;c vn  c nht m&agrave; <a href=\"https://blockchain.tso.vn/\">c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain</a> c&oacute; th gii quyt, s hiu qu h c&oacute; th mang li, v&agrave; c&aacute;c dch v m&agrave; h quan t&acirc;m m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn n s tr gi&uacute;p t c&aacute;c trung gian.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">V&iacute; d, c&aacute;c h thng cho thu&ecirc; xe hi phi tp trung ngn hn &atilde; c to ra tr&ecirc;n blockchain, gi&uacute;p th&uacute;c y c&aacute;c h thng cho thu&ecirc; ngang h&agrave;ng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn ngi trung gian.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cui c&ugrave;ng, mt trong nhng c&ocirc;ng ty c&ocirc;ng ngh ln nht v c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain l&agrave; IBM, ang hng n vic a n cho c&aacute;c doanh nghip kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&aacute;c d &aacute;n m&atilde; ngun m Hyperledger. IBM &atilde; u t hn 200 triu &ocirc; la v&agrave;o ph&aacute;t trin blockchain v&agrave; vn ang tip tc thu&ecirc; c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin blockchain t&agrave;i nng tham gia v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng ty ca h.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Nh&igrave;n v tng lai</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Khi s ph&aacute;t trin ca blockchain tip tc l&agrave; mi nhn ca cng ng Crypto, nhiu ngi t hi iu g&igrave; s xy ra tip theo? Nhiu c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t trin Blockchain s tp trung v&agrave;o 2 kh&iacute;a cnh ch&iacute;nh:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://blockchain.tso.vn/\"><em><strong>Blockchain nh mt dch v (BaaS)</strong></em></a></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BaaS l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic thit yu ca c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t trin Blockchain, cung cp c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p Blockchain cho nhng ngi mun x&acirc;y dng hoc s dng c&aacute;c ng dng th&ocirc;ng minh hoc hp ng th&ocirc;ng minh ca ri&ecirc;ng h. BaaS thng bao gm c&aacute;c dch v c bn - sau n&agrave;y kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n nn tng n&agrave;y - cung cp cho h mt nn tng vng chc  h x&acirc;y dng n&ecirc;n concept ca m&igrave;nh.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">V&iacute; d: C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty s s dng c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty BaaS  gi&uacute;p bo mt d liu ca h an to&agrave;n, ri&ecirc;ng t, kh&ocirc;ng b bin i bng c&aacute;ch s dng c&ocirc;ng ngh Blockchain. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt gii ph&aacute;p &ocirc;i b&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng c&oacute; li, v&igrave; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng sn s&agrave;ng tin tng v&agrave;o mt dch v hn nu nh bit rng n&oacute; c x&acirc;y dng da tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c hp ng th&ocirc;ng minh m&atilde; ngun m thay v&igrave; mt t chc tp trung.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong>Blockchain Lp 1 v&agrave; Lp 2 (L1 v&agrave; L2)</strong></em></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Vi vic &aacute;p dng ng&agrave;y mt nhiu v&agrave; d kin s c&ograve;n nhiu hn trong tng lai, c&aacute;c Blockchain lp 1, chng hn nh Ethereum, tt c u ang phi vt ln vi vn  ln nht: Kh nng m rng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">C&aacute;c protocol hoc framework ca Blockchain lp 2 c x&acirc;y dng da tr&ecirc;n chui hin c&oacute;  gii quyt c&aacute;c vn  v kh nng m rng v&agrave; tc . Ta c&oacute; th ly v&iacute; d l&agrave; Polygon, c x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n u chui Ethereum.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Mt khi Lp 2 c th&ocirc;ng qua, phn ln c&ocirc;ng vic kh&oacute; nhn nht c&oacute; th c g khi Lp 1 trong khi vn gi bo mt - n t c ch ng thun &atilde; chn. Vic th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o lp hai thng c gi l&agrave; gii ph&aacute;p ngo&agrave;i chui cho c&aacute;c vn  m&agrave; phn ln c&aacute;c L1 ang phi i mt.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Lp 2 n&agrave;y b&acirc;y gi &atilde; c&oacute; th tp trung v&agrave;o tc  v&agrave; kh nng m rng trong khi vn c hng li t t&iacute;nh bo mt ca L1. Mt v&iacute; d kh&aacute;c c&oacute; th c  cp n l&agrave; Polygon Network nhm m rng quy m&ocirc; ca chui blockchain Ethereum. Mt trong nhng li &iacute;ch ln nht ca Polygon l&agrave; ph&iacute; giao dch cc k r so vi Ethereum, trong khi vn gi nguy&ecirc;n t&iacute;nh bo mt ca Ethereum. C&aacute;c giao dch Polygon thng c&oacute; gi&aacute; &iacute;t hn 0.01$, thp hn rt nhiu so vi gi&aacute; 15$ ca Ethereum.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Tr&ecirc;n ht, Ethereum c&oacute; th qun l&yacute; khong 14 giao dch mi gi&acirc;y, ch l&agrave; mt phn nh ca 65.000 giao dch mi gi&acirc;y ca Polygon.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-s